un. To be clear, <strong>she is a human woman with pikachu's powers (and tail)</strong>, not a furry or pokemon. (a bit like a superhero, spiderman etc.)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>About the Scenario:</strong> She runs into you at the university. I did not define anything about you ","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"4b454667-ef97-4710-89e4-fe4846af5f81_913d12fa-952c-40a1-b9f7-97db4f269001.webp","creator":"Cynisca","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","🐙 Pokemon","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human"],"chats":2416,"messages":22586,"created_at":"2025-01-09T11:49:16.674966+00:00"}